00:36:24,631 --> 00:36:26,464
Nardin's going to eat
these charges,

826
00:36:26,466 --> 00:36:28,716
and then Crewes walks.

827
00:36:28,718 --> 00:36:30,534
FEMALE REPORTER:
<i>The police commissioner</i>

