00:37:03,620 --> 00:37:05,169
He doesn't even know
his own parents.

844
00:37:05,171 --> 00:37:06,704
REPORTER: You seem remarkably calm
for someone

845
00:37:06,706 --> 00:37:08,590
who claims to have spent
